sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Service
    participant Storage
    
    Client->>API: 1. Request
    API->>API: 2. Validate
    API->>Service: 3. Process
    Service->>Storage: 4. Read/Write
    Storage-->>Service: 5. Return data
    Service-->>API: 6. Result
    API-->>Client: 7. Response
